==English==

===Etymology===
From ''[[not]]'' + ''[[even]]''

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# {{non-gloss definition|Introduces or constitutes a more emphatic negation or exclusion than "not".}}
#: '''''Not even''' I knew that.''
#: ''You did'''n't even''' look at me.''

